data.description: Charming log cabin on 11.24 acres with a walkout basement. Enjoy rustic elegance and modern comfort. The main level features a cozy living space with a stone fireplace and large windows offering picturesque views. The walkout basement provides additional space, opening to the expansive grounds. A 40x46 outbuilding adds versatility, perfect for a workshop or storage. The property includes a serene pond, creating a peaceful retreat. With its unique blend of rustic appeal and practical amenities, this property offers a rare opportunity to embrace country living at its finest.
